import React from 'react';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom';
import Card from './Cards';


ReactDOM.render(<> 
     <Card imgsrc="https://mcmscache.epapr.in/post_images/website_350/post_19329023/thumb.jpg" //custom attribute 
         title="A Netflix Orignal Series"
         sname="Delhi crime"
         link="https://www.netflix.com/in/title/81076756"
     />
     <Card imgsrc="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/L6P3nI6VnlY/maxresdefault.jpg" //custom attribute 
         title="A Netflix Orignal Series"

         sname="Betaal"
         link="https://www.netflix.com/in/title/81076756"/>

     <Card imgsrc="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/7/7a/Sacred_Games_Title.png" //custom attribute 
         title="A Netflix Orignal Series"
         sname="Scrad Game"
         link="https://www.netflix.com/in/title/81076756"/>

     <Card imgsrc="https://spiderimg.amarujala.com/assets/images/2020/03/20/750x506/she_1584713601.png" //custom attribute 
         title="A Netflix Orignal Series"
         sname="She"
         link="https://www.netflix.com/in/title/81076756"/>
     </> ,document.getElementById("root")
